{"about_the_game":"Long ago Calla and Eris lived in harmony. Then, everything changed when the Goofy Tornadoes attacked. They swept the sheep all over the world and left two shepherds - Calla and Eris to save them. Even though our shepherds are very resilient, they have a lot of challenges before they're ready to save anyone. Are you brave enough to handle this adventure?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/extras/Wishlist.gif?t=1739135790\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/extras/en-us__TwoPlayerCoop.png?t=1739135790\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/extras/WorkTogether.gif?t=1739135790\" /><br>Engage in local 2-player coop gameplay where teamwork and communication are key to overcoming the game's obstacles.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/extras/en-us__PlaySolo.png?t=1739135790\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/extras/Solo.gif?t=1739135790\" /><br>Dive into the role of Calla or Eris, tackling unique challenges and puzzles on your own in a beautifully crafted single-player mode.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/extras/en-us__SaveTheSheep.png?t=1739135790\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/extras/SaveTheSheep.gif?t=1739135790\" /><br>Take on the hero's quest to find and save the lost sheep of your village, each uniquely adorable and awaiting rescue.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/extras/en-us__PlayWithFire.png?t=1739135790\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/extras/PlayWithFire.gif?t=1739135790\" /><br>Strategically navigate through fiery landscapes, using tools and clever thinking to manage and extinguish flames.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/extras/en-us__FunPhysics.png?t=1739135790\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/extras/Goofy.gif?t=1739135790\" /><br>Laugh along with playful physics and ragdoll effects that turn every challenge into a joyful blunder.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/extras/en-us__VisualFeast.png?t=1739135790\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/extras/Explore.gif?t=1739135790\" /><br>Traverse through artistically rich environments, where each island offers a visual treat as unique as its puzzles.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/extras/en-us__KeyFeatures.png?t=1739135790\" /><br>- Play 2-player local coop<br>- Play solo<br>- Fun Physics and Ragdolls<br>- Solve puzzles to Save Sheep from danger!<br>- Flammable and Extinguishable world<br>- Leaderboards<br>- Collect Easter Eggs<br>- Keyboard and Controller support<br>- Ultra-wide support","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739135790","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739135790","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739135790","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930170/capsule_184x69.j